# UI types

- **Shared** (used across features or by hooks + multiple components): define in `ui/types/` as focused modules (`chat.ts`, `models.ts`, etc.) and re-export from `ui/types/index.ts`. Import via `from "../types"` or `from "../../types"` as appropriate.
- **Feature-local** (one component folder, multiple files, no imports from outside that folder): put in `components/<Feature>/types.ts`.
- **Avoid duplication**: identical unions or object shapes should exist in one place (`ui/types` or the feature `types.ts`), not copy-pasted.
